
## Plot Styles
Colors, font size, linethinkness, all have default values in **matplotlib**. In addition to the default style for these plot attributes, additional styles are available to apply to **matplotlib** plots
To use the default style, either don't specify a style at all or use the line ```plt.style.use('default')``.  Remember, if using a jupyter notebook include the line ```%matplotlib inline```
